      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "description": "How players join the Trial Play event.<br/><code>launch</code>: LaunchGame with eventId, players will automatically claim on first successful launch until it reaches maxMemberCount <br/><code>bind</code>: Call <code>BindTrialPlayMembers</code> to pre-register players before they can claim on launch.",
